# Dataset: Largest Companies by Market Cap

This folder stores **local copies** of the dataset (not committed by default).  
Source: **Kaggle** – [Largest Companies by Market Cap](https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/shiivvvaam/largest-companies-by-market-cap)

## How to download (Kaggle CLI)

1) Install & authenticate:
```bash
pip install kaggle

# Kaggle → Account → Create New API Token
# Save the file kaggle.json to:
# Windows:  C:\Users\<YOU>\.kaggle\kaggle.json
# macOS/Linux:
mkdir -p ~/.kaggle
mv ~/Downloads/kaggle.json ~/.kaggle/
chmod 600 ~/.kaggle/kaggle.json
